{"title":"“梅花”与流萤","authors":["符加雷"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":7,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“梅花”与流萤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"符加雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵“梅花”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵王小松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头一次打靶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就吃了个大“烧饼”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他呀——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸红得像关公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里乱咕哝："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这……这枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恐怕有毛病！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军一旁看得清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却默默不做声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想当年："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端着一支“老套筒”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揍得敌人像鸟惊弓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能有这样一条枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨嗨！一个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能顶白匪一连兵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗思量："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我能以身作则，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是无声的命令。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见他："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"膀子一抖浑身劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老将出马”好威风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据枪瞄准，一串脆响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五个弹孔——一朵“梅花”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——开在靶心正当中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王小松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃一惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼神直发愣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又惭愧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又激动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼泪盈盈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三只流萤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王小松发愤图强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗把将军当标兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏练三伏热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬练三九冷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里雨里练眼力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜色漆黑他瞄星星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为练臂力他托砖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加了一层又一层；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人跟他开玩笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“王小松呀快改名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托塔天王叫李靖！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他郑重其事来纠正："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不不不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学就学董存瑞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——巨掌托雷霆……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军二次来考核，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他夜打“活靶”显奇功："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呯呯呯，三声脆响！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打灭了三只萤火虫……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵掌声似暴风雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神枪手按不住心头高兴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正等着将军表扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听将军喊一声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“王小松！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“到！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“耳闻夜空大雁叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪举雁落你能不能？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“暂……暂时还不行！”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“练吧，练吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让你的颗颗子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都长起耳朵和眼睛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果敌人胆敢来侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗖——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗖——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗖——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都把他们消灭干净。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}